# NSwag generated client

`clients/angular/im-cloud-api-client.ts` is **auto-generated** by NSwag (`./scripts/generate-api-client.sh`). **Never edit it manually.**

- Regenerate after backend API/DTO changes.
- In the Angular app, import from `@im-cloud/api` (npm `file:../../clients/angular`).
- Add app-specific logic in wrappers under `src/app/core/` (e.g. `auth-api.service.ts`), not in the generated file.
- `api-client.extension.ts` is merged on regenerate — keep it minimal (no duplicate exports).
